      "content": "Yeah, it's just standard procedure. The dev team says we're hitting storage limits on the long-term logs, so we have to trim the fat. Once the script hits the 3-month mark, those older preferences and guest histories are gone for good. It'll definitely streamline things, even if it means losing some of the deep background info on the regulars.",
